# Files owned by each individual collection — the template sync never touches
# these. Everything NOT listed here is kept in sync with the template repo.
# Patterns are rsync-style, anchored to the repository root.

# GitHub's built-in GITHUB_TOKEN cannot push changes under .github/workflows/
# without a PAT that has 'workflow' scope, so workflow files are not synced.
# Update them via "Use this template" for new collections, or by hand.
/.github/workflows/

/galaxy.yml
/README.md
/LICENSE
/CHANGELOG.rst
/replace.sh
/requirements.yml
/requirements.txt
/meta/
/docs/
/plugins/
/roles/
/changelogs/changelog.yaml
/changelogs/config.yaml
/changelogs/.plugin-cache.yaml
